%py_provides %oname
%py_requires zope.interface

%description
Common / shared utilities for a Pyramid web application. (Some
originally re-factored from the depreciated weblayer micro-framework).

%package tests
Summary: Tests for %oname
Group: Development/Python
Requires: %name = %EVR

%description tests
